fields.taste_profile: Bitter
fields.description:
A smooth and well-balanced coffee, Bali Roast offers delicate floral notes, hints of citrus, and a velvety body. Perfect for a serene morning ritual.



Grown in the rich volcanic soils of Bali, these Arabica beans are shade-grown and processed using the traditional wet method to enhance their vibrant flavors.

fields.taste_profile: Woody
fields.description:
This bold and earthy coffee features deep cocoa undertones with a hint of spice, delivering a strong morning kick.



Cultivated in Kenya’s warm lowlands, these Robusta beans are sun-dried through the natural process to maintain their bold character.

fields.taste_profile: Bright and floral with hints of jasmine
fields.description:
This bright and fruity coffee offers notes of citrus, honey, and a hint of jasmine, making it a perfect morning brew. Its light roast enhances the vibrant acidity, creating a delicate balance of flavors that dance on your palate.



Grown at high altitudes in the Ethiopian highlands, this coffee is cultivated by smallholder farmers who use traditional shade-growing techniques. Once harvested, the beans are meticulously processed using the washed (wet) method to preserve their vibrant flavor profile.

fields.taste_profile: Bold and smoky with a chocolatey finish
fields.description:
This dark and smoky coffee boasts rich chocolate tones with a touch of caramel sweetness, making it a night-time favorite.



Sourced from Colombia’s fertile valleys, these Robusta beans undergo a natural drying process, adding depth to their intense flavor.

fields.taste_profile: Sweet and citrusy with a honeyed aroma
fields.description:
A luxurious cup with honeyed sweetness, subtle nuttiness, and a creamy finish. Perfect for savoring at sunset.



Grown in Costa Rica’s high-altitude farms, these Arabica beans are processed using the honey method, which enhances their natural sweetness.

fields.taste_profile: Earthy and complex with nutty undertones
fields.description:
Harvest Moon offers a unique profile with bold, woody undertones and a hint of floral aroma. Its medium roast provides a rich body.

Grown in Guatemala’s rainforest regions, Liberica beans are hand-picked and semi-washed to balance their wild and robust flavors.

fields.taste_profile: Smooth and buttery with a hint of vanilla
fields.description:
A sweet and mellow coffee with hints of vanilla, coconut, and tropical fruits. Its silky texture makes every sip a delight.



Cultivated in Jamaica’s Blue Mountains, these Arabica beans are washed and sun-dried for a smooth and refined flavor.

fields.taste_profile: Rich and earthy with notes of cocoa
fields.description:
Known for its bold flavor and rich crema, this dark roasted coffee boasts earthy tones with a touch of cocoa bitterness. Its high caffeine content delivers a strong kick, perfect for espresso lovers.



Cultivated in the volcanic soils of Vietnam, these beans thrive in lower altitudes under warm, humid conditions. Farmers use the natural (dry) process to sun-dry the beans, enhancing their robust and intense flavor.

fields.taste_profile: Bright and tangy with berry notes
fields.description:
A bright and vibrant coffee with floral and citrusy notes, Morning Glory is the perfect pick-me-up for any morning.



Sourced from Kenya’s high-altitude regions, these Arabica beans are wet-processed to bring out their lively and bright flavor profile.

fields.taste_profile: Smoky and bold with a hint of spice
fields.description:
Twilight Roast delivers a bold and smoky flavor with hints of dark chocolate and toasted nuts. Its full body lingers on the palate.



Harvested in Indonesia’s rich volcanic soils, Liberica beans are semi-washed to highlight their unique and complex characteristics.

fields.taste_profile: Sweet and smooth with a hint of maple
fields.description:
Maple Morning offers a cozy cup with subtle hints of maple syrup, nuts, and a smooth, buttery finish. Perfect for cold mornings.



Produced in Canada’s temperate climate, these Arabica beans are imported and roasted locally to maintain a fresh and authentic taste.

fields.taste_profile: Strong and robust with a velvety finish
fields.description:
This luxurious espresso boasts a velvety crema, bold cocoa notes, and a deep, robust finish. Ideal for espresso aficionados.



Crafted in Italy using carefully selected Robusta beans, the beans are roasted to perfection and processed for optimal espresso quality.

fields.taste_profile: Tropical and smooth with notes of coconut
fields.description:
A tropical delight with sweet, fruity notes and a creamy body, Island Bliss captures the essence of Hawaiian paradise.



Grown on the volcanic slopes of Hawaii, these Arabica beans are shade-grown and wet-processed to bring out their tropical flavor.

fields.taste_profile: Rich and spicy with cinnamon undertones
fields.description:
Aztec Harvest offers a smooth and balanced cup with notes of chocolate, cinnamon, and a hint of spice. Perfect for cozy evenings.



Cultivated in Mexico’s mountainous regions, these Arabica beans are washed and sun-dried to retain their rich and complex flavors.

fields.taste_profile: Smoky and intense with a nutty finish
fields.description:
Polar Night is a bold and intense coffee with smoky undertones and a hint of dark caramel. Perfect for staying warm on chilly nights.



Roasted in Norway, these imported Robusta beans are dark roasted to enhance their strong and smoky profile.

fields.taste_profile: Smooth and creamy with a chocolate hint
fields.description:
A silky-smooth coffee with a creamy texture, Swiss Velvet delights with subtle chocolate notes and a nutty undertone.



These premium Arabica beans are sourced globally and roasted in Switzerland using meticulous techniques to ensure velvety perfection.

fields.taste_profile: Floral and aromatic with notes of dates
fields.description:
Sahara Breeze offers a bold, earthy flavor with hints of dried fruits and a smoky finish. It’s an adventurous coffee for the bold.



Liberica beans are grown in Egypt’s desert oases, where they are hand-picked and sun-dried to create their unique, full-bodied taste.

fields.taste_profile: Bright, citrus, floral
fields.description: A light roast coffee that captures the bright, citrusy essence of Ethiopian beans. Perfect for pour-over enthusiasts.

fields.taste_profile: Bold, earthy, nutty
fields.description: A bold, dark roast with a strong caffeine kick. Ideal for espresso lovers.

fields.taste_profile: Fruity, smoky, floral
fields.description: A rare and exotic coffee with a unique flavor profile. A must-try for adventurous coffee drinkers.

fields.taste_profile: Tart, fruity, complex
fields.description: A complex coffee with tart and fruity notes. Excelsa beans bring an unexpected twist to your cup.

fields.taste_profile: Notes of citrus, caramel sweetness, and a smooth finish.
fields.description:
Sunrise Arabica Blend is a testament to the vibrant coffee culture of Colombia. Sourced from high-altitude farms, this coffee offers a delicate balance of citrus brightness and caramel sweetness. The light roast preserves the bean's natural flavors, delivering a cup that's lively and refreshing. Ideal for those who enjoy nuanced and elegant coffee experiences. 

The beans are handpicked at peak ripeness and processed with meticulous care. Farmers employ a washed method that enhances clarity of flavor while preserving the coffee's inherent brightness. Every sip carries the essence of sustainable farming practices and the passion of Colombian coffee artisans.

fields.taste_profile: Rich, earthy, and bold with a dark chocolate finish.
fields.description:
Velvet Robusta Espresso offers a bold and intense experience for lovers of strong coffee. This robusta blend from Vietnam is characterized by its rich earthy undertones and a deep, dark chocolate finish. Perfect for espresso-based drinks or those who enjoy a powerful morning brew. 

The beans are grown on family-run farms using traditional cultivation techniques. After harvest, they undergo a natural drying process that intensifies their bold flavor profile. Velvet Robusta Espresso is a tribute to Vietnam's thriving coffee heritage and commitment to quality.

fields.taste_profile: Fruity, tart, with hints of dark berries and a subtle spiciness.
fields.description:
Excelsa Heritage Roast captures the unique and complex flavors of excelsa beans grown in the Philippines. This medium roast brings out the fruity tartness and subtle dark berry notes, balanced by a gentle spiciness. A truly distinctive coffee for those who appreciate variety and depth in their cup. 

Excelsa farmers in the Philippines take pride in their organic cultivation methods, ensuring that each bean reflects the region's diverse terroir. The coffee is sun-dried and slow-roasted to perfection, creating a flavor journey that celebrates the region's coffee traditions.

fields.taste_profile: Floral, woody, with a honey-like sweetness and exotic aroma.
fields.description:
Golden Liberica Reserve is an exotic offering that showcases the distinctive characteristics of liberica beans. With its floral and woody undertones, this coffee is accented by a honey-like sweetness and an aroma that is both bold and enchanting. Ideal for those seeking a rare and luxurious coffee experience. 

The beans are cultivated in the lush highlands of Malaysia, where they are naturally sun-dried to enhance their complex profile. Artisanal roasting techniques ensure that each batch captures the unique essence of liberica coffee, making every sip a memorable journey.

fields.taste_profile: Smooth, nutty, with caramel and milk chocolate undertones.
fields.description:
Harvest Blend Espresso is a harmonious blend of Brazilian arabica beans, offering a smooth and nutty profile with delightful caramel and milk chocolate undertones. The medium roast enhances its natural sweetness, making it a perfect choice for espresso enthusiasts and latte lovers. 

Grown in the fertile soils of Brazil's coffee belt, the beans are hand-harvested and processed using a semi-washed method. This traditional approach preserves the beans' natural sugars, resulting in a rich and balanced coffee that showcases Brazil's coffee-growing expertise.

fields.taste_profile: Bright, floral, with notes of jasmine and bergamot.
fields.description:
Highland Sunrise Arabica is a stunning coffee sourced from the highlands of Ethiopia, the birthplace of coffee. This light roast preserves the bean's delicate floral notes, featuring jasmine and bergamot, with a bright, clean finish. Perfect for pour-over brewing methods to highlight its intricate flavor profile. 

Cultivated by smallholder farmers who employ traditional growing practices, this coffee represents centuries of expertise. Each bean is hand-picked, washed, and sun-dried on raised beds, ensuring exceptional quality in every cup.

fields.taste_profile: Bold, earthy, with a hint of nutmeg and dark cocoa.
fields.description:
Rainforest Robusta Reserve is a bold and earthy coffee that embodies the spirit of Uganda's lush landscapes. Its dark roast highlights the robusta bean's natural strength, with a hint of nutmeg and dark cocoa adding depth to each sip. Ideal for strong coffee lovers or as a base for creamy lattes. 

Sustainably grown in rainforest regions, this coffee supports both environmental preservation and local farming communities. Its rich flavor is a testament to the care taken during cultivation and artisanal roasting.

fields.taste_profile: Tart, fruity, with hints of plum and exotic spices.
fields.description:
Pacific Excelsa Delight offers a unique taste experience with its tart, fruity profile and subtle hints of plum and exotic spices. This medium roast coffee is as bold as it is intricate, making it a favorite for adventurous coffee enthusiasts. 

Hailing from Indonesia's volcanic soils, these excelsa beans are grown in harmony with nature. Farmers use traditional methods, allowing the coffee's distinctive characteristics to shine through. A sip of Pacific Excelsa Delight transports you to the heart of Indonesia.

fields.taste_profile: Woody, floral, with a touch of tropical fruit sweetness.
fields.description:
Amber Liberica Essence showcases the rare and exotic liberica bean, delivering a woody and floral profile with a touch of tropical fruit sweetness. This medium roast is carefully crafted to highlight its rich and complex nature, making it an unforgettable coffee experience. 

Grown in the unique climate of India's coffee regions, this liberica coffee is harvested with care and processed using traditional methods. The result is a coffee that stands out for its distinctive aroma and bold flavor, perfect for special moments.

fields.taste_profile: Smooth, chocolatey, with subtle citrus and nutty undertones.
fields.description:
Velvet Morning Blend is a Guatemalan masterpiece that combines smooth chocolatey notes with subtle citrus and nutty undertones. This medium roast is perfect for those seeking a balanced and versatile coffee that shines in any brewing method. 

Grown on family-run farms in Guatemala's fertile highlands, this arabica coffee is cultivated with sustainability and quality in mind. The beans are washed and sun-dried, capturing the essence of Guatemalan coffee culture in every cup.

fields.taste_profile: Rich, caramel-like sweetness with hints of red berries and citrus.
fields.description:
Crimson Harvest Arabica is a Colombian treasure that boasts a rich, caramel-like sweetness intertwined with subtle notes of red berries and citrus. This medium roast strikes a perfect balance between brightness and depth, making it ideal for coffee lovers who appreciate a nuanced flavor profile. 

Grown in Colombia's renowned coffee-growing regions, the beans are cultivated at high altitudes, where the cooler climate enhances their complexity. Hand-picked and meticulously processed, Crimson Harvest delivers an exceptional coffee experience, cup after cup.

fields.taste_profile: Bright, tangy, with tropical fruit and toasted almond notes.
fields.description:
Tropical Dawn Excelsa offers a vibrant coffee experience with its bright, tangy profile featuring tropical fruit and toasted almond undertones. This light roast preserves the unique character of excelsa beans, making it a refreshing and exotic choice for adventurous coffee drinkers. 

Sourced from Vietnam's verdant coffee plantations, these beans are grown in harmony with the natural environment. The careful attention to cultivation and processing ensures a coffee that is as sustainable as it is flavorful.

fields.taste_profile: Intense, earthy, with dark chocolate and smoky overtones.
fields.description:
Midnight Velvet Robusta is an intense and earthy coffee that features dark chocolate and smoky overtones, perfect for those who crave a bold, full-bodied brew. This dark roast brings out the robust flavor characteristics that make robusta beans stand apart. 

Cultivated in India's shaded coffee estates, these beans are grown with a deep respect for nature and tradition. Each cup of Midnight Velvet Robusta is a tribute to the hardworking farmers and the rich heritage of Indian coffee.

fields.taste_profile: Unique, woody, with floral notes and a subtle fruity sweetness.
fields.description:
Amber Glow Liberica showcases the rare and aromatic liberica bean, known for its distinctive woody profile, floral notes, and a touch of fruity sweetness. This medium roast enhances the bean’s complex flavor, offering a coffee experience unlike any other. 

Sourced from the Philippines, Amber Glow Liberica celebrates the country's rich coffee history and biodiversity. The beans are hand-harvested and carefully processed to ensure the highest quality, making it a true gem for coffee enthusiasts.

fields.taste_profile: Smooth, nutty, with hints of honey and orange zest.
fields.description:
Golden Peaks Blend is a Costa Rican delight that features a smooth and nutty flavor profile, complemented by hints of honey and orange zest. This medium roast is versatile, making it perfect for both everyday enjoyment and special occasions. 

Grown in Costa Rica's lush highlands, this arabica coffee is a product of sustainable farming practices. The dedication of local farmers shines through in every sip, offering a taste of Costa Rica’s pristine landscapes and vibrant coffee culture.

fields.taste_profile: Floral, bright acidity, with hints of jasmine and stone fruit.
fields.description:
Highland Bloom Arabica is a delicate and vibrant coffee from Ethiopia, the birthplace of coffee itself. This light roast celebrates the natural floral and fruity notes of arabica beans, with a bright acidity and lingering hints of jasmine and stone fruit. 

Cultivated at high altitudes and processed with care, Highland Bloom captures the essence of Ethiopia’s rich coffee heritage. Each sip offers a sensory journey to the lush Ethiopian highlands, where coffee cultivation is a centuries-old art form.

fields.taste_profile: Tangy, tropical, with subtle spice and chocolate notes.
fields.description:
Pacific Sunset Excelsa is a tropical coffee adventure, delivering tangy and fruity flavors with subtle undertones of spice and chocolate. This medium roast enhances the unique character of excelsa beans, providing a bold yet balanced cup. 

Grown in the volcanic soils of Indonesia, these beans are nurtured in a diverse and fertile environment. With every sip, Pacific Sunset invites you to experience the vibrant and dynamic flavors of the Pacific Rim.

fields.taste_profile: Strong, earthy, with hints of molasses and roasted nuts.
fields.description:
Bold Horizon Robusta is a full-bodied and robust coffee that delivers strong, earthy flavors with a rich finish of molasses and roasted nuts. This dark roast emphasizes the strength and depth of robusta beans, perfect for those who enjoy a powerful cup of coffee. 

Grown in Uganda’s fertile coffee regions, these beans reflect the dedication of smallholder farmers who rely on coffee as a cornerstone of their livelihoods. Bold Horizon is a testament to their craftsmanship and Uganda's coffee legacy.

fields.taste_profile: Exotic, fruity, with notes of jackfruit and wildflowers.
fields.description:
Golden Orchard Liberica is an exotic offering with fruity notes of jackfruit and a fragrant bouquet of wildflowers. This medium roast allows the liberica beans’ natural complexity to shine, creating a truly memorable coffee experience. 

Grown in the rich, tropical soils of Malaysia, these liberica beans are a rare and cherished find. Golden Orchard Liberica brings a touch of the extraordinary to your coffee routine, celebrating the diversity of global coffee cultures.

fields.taste_profile: Smooth, chocolatey, with caramel sweetness and a hint of citrus.
fields.description:
Velvet Hills Arabica Blend is a harmonious combination of smooth chocolatey notes, caramel sweetness, and a hint of bright citrus. This medium roast strikes a balance between indulgence and brightness, making it a versatile choice for any occasion. 

Sourced from the lush coffee-growing regions of Guatemala, Velvet Hills reflects the country’s dedication to high-quality coffee production. Each cup offers a taste of Guatemala’s rich agricultural traditions and scenic landscapes.

fields.taste_profile: Smokey and bitter
fields.description: Epic 15 is our trademark coffee. We'd serve this to anyone we wanted to impress.

fields.about:
Roaster's Delight is a celebration of the art and science of coffee roasting. Founded in 2010, the company is dedicated to producing small-batch, hand-roasted coffee that delights the senses. Their team of expert roasters meticulously monitors every stage of the process, ensuring that each bean reaches its full potential. Roaster's Delight’s offers a wide range of blends and single-origin coffees, catering to both traditional tastes and adventurous palates. From light floral notes to deep, smoky undertones, their coffees are a testament to their expertise and passion.

At the heart of Roaster's Delight’s ethos is a commitment to sustainability and community. They source beans from farms that prioritize ethical and eco-friendly practices, ensuring a positive impact on both the environment and the lives of farmers. Roaster's Delight’s also invests in community programs, supporting initiatives that promote education and economic development in coffee-growing regions. By combining quality, ethics, and innovation, Roaster's Delight’s has become a trusted name in specialty coffee.

Espresso X is a bold and modern coffee brand that has redefined the espresso experience. Since its inception in 2010, Espresso X has focused exclusively on crafting the perfect espresso shot. Known for its dark, rich roasts and intense flavor profiles, the brand has gained a cult following among espresso lovers. Espresso X started as a boutique café in Milan, Italy, and quickly expanded internationally, becoming synonymous with premium espresso and sleek, contemporary design. Their dedication to excellence has earned them accolades and a reputation for uncompromising quality.

Espresso X combines traditional Italian roasting techniques with cutting-edge technology to deliver an unparalleled coffee experience. The company sources its beans from high-altitude farms, ensuring the cherries mature slowly and develop deep, complex flavors. Each batch is roasted in small quantities to preserve freshness and maintain precision. Espresso X is also a pioneer in eco-conscious practices, utilizing energy-efficient roasting methods and biodegradable packaging. By marrying heritage with sustainability, Espresso X has created a brand that appeals to both purists and modern coffee enthusiasts alike.

Java Experts was established in the mid-2000s with a mission to demystify the art of coffee brewing. Founded by a group of seasoned baristas and coffee connoisseurs, the company has become a trusted name in the specialty coffee world. Java Experts prides itself on its educational approach, offering workshops, guides, and curated coffee blends designed to help enthusiasts elevate their coffee-making skills. From sourcing premium beans to developing innovative brewing tools, Java Experts ensures every aspect of the coffee experience is exceptional. Their flagship roasts, which balance complex flavor notes with a smooth finish, have earned a loyal following among coffee aficionados worldwide.

What sets Java Experts apart is its dedication to education and innovation. The company partners with small-scale farmers across the globe, focusing on direct trade relationships that promote sustainability and transparency. Each batch of coffee undergoes meticulous testing to ensure peak flavor and consistency. Java Experts’s roasting team employs a unique profiling method that highlights the distinct characteristics of each bean. By blending tradition with modern expertise, Java Experts empowers its customers to craft café-quality coffee from the comfort of their homes.

Latte Pro is a trailblazer in the world of artisan coffee, renowned for its expertise in crafting the perfect latte. Founded in 2008 by a team of visionary baristas, the company has become synonymous with luxurious, velvety coffee beverages. Latte Pro specializes in blends that pair seamlessly with milk, elevating the flavors of their espresso-based drinks to an art form. Their signature latte blends, meticulously roasted to achieve balance and complexity, have garnered widespread acclaim from both professionals and home brewers. Latte Pro's mission is simple: to make the latte experience accessible to everyone, without compromising on quality or creativity.

At the heart of LatteP ro’s success is its dedication to innovation and sustainability. The company partners directly with small-scale coffee farmers, ensuring fair trade practices while sourcing the finest beans. Latte Pro employs cutting-edge roasting techniques to preserve the unique characteristics of each origin, emphasizing the harmony between coffee and milk. Committed to reducing its environmental footprint, LattePro utilizes eco-friendly packaging and supports reforestation projects in coffee-growing regions. This holistic approach, combined with a relentless passion for coffee, has solidified LattePro's reputation as a leader in the specialty coffee industry.

Java World is a household name in the global coffee scene, celebrated for its approachable yet sophisticated blends. Established in 2005, the company began as a small roastery catering to local cafes but quickly gained a loyal following for its commitment to quality and consistency. JavaWorld is dedicated to bringing the joy of coffee to every corner of the world, offering a diverse range of roasts that cater to all palates—from light and fruity to dark and bold. Their carefully curated blends strike the perfect balance between accessibility and complexity, making them a favorite among both casual drinkers and connoisseurs.

What sets Java World apart is its commitment to building connections—between people, cultures, and the environment. The company sources beans from diverse regions, celebrating the unique flavors each origin has to offer. Through direct trade relationships, Java World supports sustainable farming practices and empowers coffee-growing communities. Their team of expert roasters applies precise profiling techniques to highlight the nuances of each bean, ensuring a consistently exceptional cup. Java World’s blend of tradition, innovation, and community engagement has made it a trusted name in coffee, beloved by enthusiasts across the globe.

Coffee Roast Co. has been a beacon for coffee enthusiasts since its inception in 2010. Known for its dedication to delivering freshly roasted coffee, the company’s mission is to bring the rich, authentic taste of expertly crafted coffee to every cup. Coffee Roast Co. specializes in small-batch roasting, ensuring that every bean reaches its peak flavor profile before making its way to customers. With a focus on single-origin offerings and expertly blended roasts, Coffee Roast Co. appeals to both the everyday coffee lover and the seasoned aficionado. Their motto, "From Bean to Cup," reflects their commitment to quality at every step of the process.

The backbone of Coffee Roast Co.'s success lies in its strong partnerships with coffee farmers around the globe. By sourcing directly from growers who practice sustainable and ethical farming methods, Coffee Roast Co. guarantees the highest quality beans while fostering positive relationships with farming communities. Their state-of-the-art roasting facilities are powered by environmentally conscious technology, underscoring their dedication to reducing their carbon footprint. Coffee Roast Co.'s commitment to transparency, quality, and environmental stewardship has earned it a loyal customer base and a reputation as one of the most reliable names in specialty coffee.

Caffeine Co. is the go-to brand for coffee lovers who crave bold, energizing flavors. Founded in 2012, the company has carved a niche for itself by offering high-caffeine blends that don’t compromise on taste. Whether it’s a morning pick-me-up or fuel for a late-night study session, Caffeine Co. delivers coffee that packs a punch. Their expertly crafted blends combine beans from high-altitude regions, resulting in a robust and complex flavor profile that invigorates the senses. Caffeine Co.'s approach is all about celebrating the power of coffee as both a ritual and a source of inspiration.

What makes Caffeine Co. unique is its focus on innovation and community. The company constantly experiments with new roast profiles and brewing techniques, ensuring that their offerings remain fresh and exciting. Caffeine Co. also prioritizes sustainable sourcing practices, working closely with farmers who use eco-friendly methods. Their commitment to community extends beyond the coffee farm; Caffeine Co. actively supports local initiatives and charities that promote education and social equity. With a passion for coffee and a dedication to making a positive impact, Caffeine Co. has become a favorite among those who view coffee as more than just a beverage—it’s a way of life.

Brew Craft stands at the intersection of tradition and innovation, offering coffee enthusiasts an unparalleled brewing experience. Founded in 2008, BrewCraft’s mission has been to empower coffee lovers with the tools and knowledge to create their perfect cup at home. From meticulously sourced beans to expertly crafted brewing guides, BrewCraft provides a comprehensive coffee journey. Their signature blends, designed for various brewing methods such as pour-over, French press, and espresso, reflect their commitment to quality and versatility. Each batch of coffee is roasted with precision, ensuring consistency in every sip.

Brew Craft’s philosophy is rooted in sustainability and education. They work directly with smallholder farmers who use eco-friendly practices, ensuring that every bean is ethically sourced. BrewCraft’s dedication to teaching its customers the art of coffee preparation has led to the creation of an extensive library of tutorials, workshops, and resources. By blending a love for coffee with a passion for craftsmanship, BrewCraft has built a community that values the process as much as the product.

Global Coffee Supply has redefined the coffee supply chain since its establishment in 2015. With a mission to bring high-quality coffee to businesses and individuals alike, they specialize in sourcing premium beans from around the world. GlobalCoffeeSupply’s extensive network of suppliers and farmers enables them to offer a diverse selection of beans, from rare micro-lots to reliable staples. Their streamlined logistics and commitment to quality control ensure that every batch arrives fresh and flavorful, ready to brew.

What sets Global Coffee Supply apart is its dedication to innovation and sustainability. By leveraging technology, they’ve optimized their sourcing and distribution processes, reducing waste and environmental impact. The company also champions fair trade practices, ensuring that farmers receive equitable compensation for their hard work. Whether serving a small café or a global chain, GlobalCoffeeSupply remains steadfast in its mission to connect people with exceptional coffee while supporting the communities that grow it.

Bean Masters is synonymous with excellence in coffee roasting. Established in 2005, this company has become a favorite among connoisseurs for its focus on single-origin beans and artisan roasting techniques. BeanMaster’s approach is deeply personal—each roast is tailored to highlight the unique characteristics of the beans, from fruity Ethiopian profiles to rich, chocolatey Colombian flavors. Their commitment to showcasing the natural beauty of coffee has earned them a reputation for producing some of the most flavorful brews on the market.

Bean Masters prides itself on transparency and sustainability. By forging direct relationships with farmers and cooperatives, they ensure that growers receive fair compensation for their work. The company also invests in eco-friendly roasting technology, minimizing its environmental impact. BeanMaster’s passion for quality extends to its customers, with a focus on education through workshops and tastings. For those who seek a coffee experience that’s both ethical and extraordinary, BeanMaster delivers.

Coffee Gang is a tenacious roastery based in Riga, Latvia. We're focused on crafting the tastiest damn coffee beans anywhere in the Baltic, using techniques gathered from all over the world.

Our founder, Kristaps has three basic principles for a proper cup of coffee: 1) Deep flavour 2) Smoky aroma 3) Good company!
